name: International Summit on Genomics and Proteomics
content: The organizer of the Global Conference Series LLC Ltd invites all participants from all over the world to join the famous scientific International Summit on Genomics and Proteomics," which will take place in Dublin, Ireland on September 19-20, 2022\. It is one of the world's most prestigious scientific conferences, hosting scientific sessions and sub-sessions on cutting-edge research and the most recent innovations in the fields of Proteomics and Genomics from all over the world. Attendees will get access to certain unique workshops and panel discussions on the most recent developments in Genomics and Proteomics.
